There's nothing left to salvage.

6
00:00:29.733 --> 00:00:33.121
I'll take a wagon into town.
get some supplies.

7
00:00:33.145 --> 00:00:34.858
No.

8
00:00:36.025 --> 00:00:37.358
We go...

9
00:00:38.442 --> 00:00:39.915
back to Chinatown.

10
00:00:40.928 --> 00:00:42.554
